text: Pervoye Maya () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tatarobashmakovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 127 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Pervoye Maya, Astrakhan Oblast
